column1: # target       : target A used in single ratio
# singleR_A_ca40_mf   : single ratio of target A_MF / Ca40_MF (per proton)
# singleR_A_ca40_src  : single ratio of target A_SRC / Ca40_SRC (per proton)
# doubleR      : double ratio of target A(SRC/MF) relative to Ca40 (SRC/MF)
# _norm_syst_err : absolute systematic error due to normalization correction factors (a) hms/shms track efficiencies (b) live time (c) proton transmission (d) ca 40/48 cntm)
# _RC_syst_err   : absolute systematic error due to radiative corrections
# _cut_syst_err  : absolute systematic error due to cut sensitivity
# _syst_err      : absolute systematic errors added in quadrature
# _tot_err       : absolute total errors (statistical + systematics added in quadrature)
# N: Z: A      : # of neutrons (N): protons(Z): nucleons (A): for target A
